edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.repository.jena

Class JenaFormatMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.repository.jena.JenaFormatMapper

  • public final class JenaFormatMapper
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the central point where are formats that should be usable by Jena are registered. Both incoming and outgoing formats must be registered here.

    Attention: This only indicates triple store support. Depending on the configuration of the server additional validators may be needed for input formats and Formatters for output formats.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Matthias Dressel, Michael Hitzker, Markus Hoefler, Andreas Loeffler, Timo Schmidt
